      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Martin Bauer</b>\n</p><p><b>Martin Bauer</b>,<br />\na German computer scientist and software developer. Graduated from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_T%C3%BCbingen\">University of Tübingen</a>, he is executive and co-founder of the IT service provider <i>Bauer &amp; Schweitzer GbR</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>  <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nWhile interested in computer chess and games during the early 2000s, Martin Bauer ported <a href=\"/Dieter_Steinwender\" title=\"Dieter Steinwender\">Steinwender's</a> and <a href=\"/Chrilly_Donninger\" title=\"Chrilly Donninger\">Donninger's</a> <a href=\"/Basic\" title=\"Basic\">Basic</a> program <a href=\"/Minimax_(program)\" title=\"Minimax (program)\">Minimax</a> to <a href=\"/Delphi\" title=\"Delphi\">Delphi</a>, \nmade it compliant to the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> protocol, and further enhanced it as <a href=\"/DelphiMax\" title=\"DelphiMax\">DelphiMax</a>. \nMartin further distributed his  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shareware\">shareware</a> chess tournament management program <i>Chessworks</i> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Bauer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=243640\">Exact value of second best move in AlphaBeta with aspiration Window</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Bauer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 01, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=224455\">Delphi and the UCI Protokoll</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Bauer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 18, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Delphi\" title=\"Delphi\">Delphi</a>, <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=225107\">One more time Delphi and UCI</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Bauer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 21, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=274620\">Check Extension</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Bauer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 03, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">Check Extensions</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Bauer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://bauer-schweitzer.de/\">Home - EDV-Schorndorf</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20160307143139if_/http://bauer-schweitzer.de/index.html?minimax/index_minimax.html\">Bauer &amp; Schweitzer - Webdesign, Software, Shareware, Freeware, EDV - MiniMAX and DelphiMax</a> (German, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, March 2016)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Bauer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gesellschaft_b%C3%BCrgerlichen_Rechts_%28Deutschland%29\">Gesellschaft bürgerlichen Rechts (Deutschland) GbR - Wikipedia.de</a> (German)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://bauer-schweitzer.de/\">Home - EDV-Schorndorf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080331031658if_/http://www.bauer-schweitzer.de:80/index.html?chesswks/index_chesswks.html\">Bauer &amp; Schweitzer - Webdesign, Software, Shareware, Freeware, EDV - Chessworks</a> (German, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, March 2008)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301022454\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 byte